headline.print_headline: Jet Stowaway to Undergo Mental Health Exam
headline.main: Jet Stowaway to Undergo Mental Health Exam

lead_paragraph: A woman who was ordered to stay away from Los Angeles International Airport after she flew from San Jose without a ticket will undergo a mental health exam.
